<h1>About This Project</h1>
<p>This application uses data from multiple sources:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Faker:</strong> Generates random authors and books.</li>
  <li><strong>CSV:</strong> Imports a list of genres.</li>
  <li><strong>JSON:</strong> Imports a set of tags.</li>
</ul>
<p>The database schema and associations (one-to-many and many-to-many) are demonstrated using this data.</p>
